  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The proposed study aims to examine several iterations of the Influenza Best Practice Alert at
      NYU Langone Health. The goal is to increase ordering of the influenza vaccine through the
      alert.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
